{"tid":818481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 將軍澳地盤3兄弟遭吊斗壓傷　27歲孻弟命危","createTime":"2018-09-14T06:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T09:06:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a0931ee2bf73c65bff35249b2dedc260998fb8","tid":818481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180914/photo/bkn-20180914095825718-0914_00822_001_05b.jpg?20180914135438\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180914%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180914095825718-0914_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20180914135438&h=ebb1dc07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳康城路1號日出康城地盤，今早(14日)9時19分，警方接報指一運載混凝土的吊斗，吊運期間鐵鏈突然斷開，吊斗墮下壓傷3名工人，其中一人當場陷入昏迷，救護員趕至，為3名姓黃(27、30及33歲)傷者分別頭及手受傷，送往伊利沙伯醫院及將軍澳醫院急救，其中27歲傷者昏迷，需留醫深切治療部病房。警方正展開調查，案件暫列工業意外，並通知勞工處到場跟進。據悉，3名傷者為兄弟關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180914/bkn-20180914095825718-0914_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180914%2Fbkn-20180914095825718-0914_00822_001.html&d=prQzaSRThAvUF1LR3lMCpP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=930b7de3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180914/bkn-20180914095825718-0914_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"983543da9d9c8811fbea812d61b8107f717c21d9","tid":818481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"吊運期間鐵鏈突然斷開<br />\n吊運期間鐵鏈突然斷開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d2f53f4ce9e50b3ce876e951bea066615b0757","tid":818481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c5e4ede05add79